<HL>
   United Student Aid Funds Is Selected
   To Take Over HEAF's Loan Portfolio
   ----
   By Kenneth H. Bacon
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/21/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
